alvarionAAAClientMIB.name: alvarionAAAClientMIB
alvarionAAAClientMIB.contactinfo: Alvarion Ltd. Postal: 21a HaBarzel St. P.O. Box 13139 Tel-Aviv 69710 Israel Phone: +972 3 645 6262

alvarionAAAProfileTable.name: alvarionAAAProfileTable
alvarionAAAProfileTable.description: A table defining the AAA server profiles currently configured on the device.

alvarionAAAProfileEntry.name: alvarionAAAProfileEntry
alvarionAAAProfileEntry.description: A AAA server profile configured in the device. alvarionAAAProfileIndex - Uniquely identifies the profile within the profile table.

alvarionAAAProfileIndex.name: alvarionAAAProfileIndex
alvarionAAAProfileIndex.description: Specifies the index of the AAA server profile.

alvarionAAAProfileName.name: alvarionAAAProfileName
alvarionAAAProfileName.description: Specifies the name of the AAA server profile.

alvarionAAAProfilePrimaryServerIndex.name: alvarionAAAProfilePrimaryServerIndex
alvarionAAAProfilePrimaryServerIndex.description: Indicates the index number of the primary server profile in the table. A value of zero indicates that no AAA server is defined.

alvarionAAAProfileSecondaryServerIndex.name: alvarionAAAProfileSecondaryServerIndex
alvarionAAAProfileSecondaryServerIndex.description: Indicates the index number of the secondary server profile in the table. A value of zero indicates that no AAA server is defined.

alvarionAAAServerTable.name: alvarionAAAServerTable
alvarionAAAServerTable.description: A table containing the AAA servers currently configured on the device.

alvarionAAAServerEntry.name: alvarionAAAServerEntry
alvarionAAAServerEntry.description: An AAA server configured on the device. alvarionAAAServerIndex - Uniquely identifies a server inside the server table.

alvarionAAAServerIndex.name: alvarionAAAServerIndex
alvarionAAAServerIndex.description: Specifies the index of the AAA server in the table.

alvarionAAAAuthenProtocol.name: alvarionAAAAuthenProtocol
alvarionAAAAuthenProtocol.description: Indicates the protocol used by the AAA client to communicate with the AAA server.

alvarionAAAAuthenMethod.name: alvarionAAAAuthenMethod
alvarionAAAAuthenMethod.description: Indicates the authentication method used by the AAA client to authenticate users via the AAA server.

alvarionAAAServerName.name: alvarionAAAServerName
alvarionAAAServerName.description: Specifies the IP address of the AAA server. The string must be a valid IP address in the format 'nnn.nnn.nnn.nnn' Where 'nnn' is a number in the range [0..255]. The '.' character is mandatory between the fields.

alvarionAAASharedSecret.name: alvarionAAASharedSecret
alvarionAAASharedSecret.description: Specifies the shared secret used by the AAA client and the AAA server. This attribute should only be set if AAA traffic between the AAA client and server is sent through a VPN tunnel. Reading this attribute will always return a zero-length string.

alvarionAAAAuthenticationPort.name: alvarionAAAAuthenticationPort
alvarionAAAAuthenticationPort.description: Indicates the port number used by the AAA client to send authentication requests to the AAA server.

alvarionAAAAccountingPort.name: alvarionAAAAccountingPort
alvarionAAAAccountingPort.description: Indicates the port number used by the AAA client to send accounting information to the AAA server.

alvarionAAATimeout.name: alvarionAAATimeout
alvarionAAATimeout.description: Indicates how long the AAA client will wait for an answer to an authentication request.

alvarionAAANASId.name: alvarionAAANASId
alvarionAAANASId.description: Indicates the network access server ID to be sent by the AAA client in each authentication request sent to the AAA server.

alvarionAAAClientMIBCompliance.name: alvarionAAAClientMIBCompliance
alvarionAAAClientMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the Alvarion AAA client MIB.

alvarionAAAProfileMIBGroup.name: alvarionAAAProfileMIBGroup
alvarionAAAProfileMIBGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the AAA profile capability.

alvarionAAAClientMIBGroup.name: alvarionAAAClientMIBGroup
alvarionAAAClientMIBGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the AAA client MIB capability.
